# S167: pipeline staging copy of salem_tiles.sqlite.
# The canonical copy that ships lives at app-salem/src/main/assets/salem_tiles.sqlite
# and IS committed — fresh clones need it to build a working APK. The staging
# copy under tools/tile-bake/dist/ is just the output of trim-to-salem.py and
# can always be regenerated.
tools/tile-bake/dist/salem_tiles.sqlite
